From 294e2d3a68c84edbd246a9393c732ebf07bc7cc6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Matheus Sampaio Queiroga <srherobrine20@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 16 Jul 2026 07:33:39 -0300
Subject: [PATCH 4/4] feat: add efficient live issue updates

Avoid re-rendering the complete timeline every two seconds and do not morph
all comments when a page first opens. Use mutation invalidations for common
issue actions, resume disconnected pages from stable content hashes, retain a
low-frequency safety refresh, preserve the visible scroll anchor and bind every
connection to Gitea's graceful-shutdown context.

Signed-off-by: Matheus Sampaio Queiroga <srherobrine20@gmail.com>
